{"tid":546798,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[十字固女皇]Ronda Rousey離開MMA簽約WWE","createTime":"2018-02-01T00:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T19:51:11.000Z","uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49d1d9a2a1525bd315f122025d2b33b324994214","tid":546798,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T00:00:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/154710?utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=sports\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F154710%3Futm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dsports&d=zEBK3YvARoZsHEwA%2BxTlJUjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=c9eeca08\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/154710?utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=sports</a><br />\n<br />\nRonda Rousey離開MMA簽約WWE　承認兩個項目截然不同<br />\n<br />\n「十字固女皇」Ronda Rousey復出，卻不是在綜合格鬥（MMA），而是轉戰美國職業摔角（WWE）。她簽約後承認WWE較像演員，然而有些早前不敢在UFC做的動作，終於有機會在台上「解鎖」。<br />\n<br />\nMMA回歸戰48秒吞2連敗<br />\n<br />\n現年30歲的Ronda Rousey自2011年加入UFC出戰MMA成為首屆女子冠軍，首12戰全勝一度稱霸。在當中最快為2015年2月只用了14秒便擊敗了Cat Zingano。Ronda Rousey在UFC193敗於Holly Holm，13個月後在UFC207的回歸，開賽48秒便敗於Amanda Nunes拳下。<br />\n<br />\n外號「Rowdy」向Roddy Piper致敬<br />\n<br />\n昨天「十字固女皇」Ronda Rousey宣布與WWE簽約，她接受ESPN訪問時承認兩個項目截然不同︰「這就是我現在的人生，也是未來幾年最重要的事。WWE不是smash and grab，更似是宣傳噱頭。我曾告訴（職業摔角手）Triple H，我可以做其他事並且賺更多錢，不過不會如此享受。WWE很有趣像做戲，摔角時我有些動作很想做，現在終於有機會，我的感覺像回到6歲時。」她將以外號「Rowdy」出戰WWE，這名字是向已故傳奇摔角手Roddy Piper致敬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.f4wonline.com/sites/www.f4wonline.com/files/field/image/rouseymania_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.f4wonline.com%2Fsites%2Fwww.f4wonline.com%2Ffiles%2Ffield%2Fimage%2Frouseymania_0.jpg&h=89e80282&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"710427a2a35129d14bb0ca500774543a75be31b2","tid":546798,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/APb0NVR2nZFtzcRx3DcsHMlr64g=/0x0:3600x2489/1200x800/filters:focal(1732x507:2308x1083)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/58483721/846238464.jpg.0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FAPb0NVR2nZFtzcRx3DcsHMlr64g%3D%2F0x0%3A3600x2489%2F1200x800%2Ffilters%3Afocal%281732x507%3A2308x1083%29%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_image%2Fimage%2F58483721%2F846238464.jpg.0.jpg&h=94507755&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32f19c0697a2eb78485b79e0655fe16a288a74ef","tid":546798,"uid":19643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T19:51:11.000Z","msg":"好可惜 佢柔道技術係mma發揮得好好"}]}